Package edu.wpi.cs3733.d20.teamk.mortuary

Class MortuaryRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.cs3733.d20.teamk.mortuary.MortuaryRequest
  • public class MortuaryRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Mortuary Request represents a request to the mortuary.

    Mortuary requests are for a specific deceased person and contains details about their death along with the employee who created the request.
